10. **F11 BonusContextSource trait** (the DEC-0008 §4 dependency-inversion seam — UCIL-owned, NOT a re-export of any external wire format):
    ```rust
    pub trait BonusContextSource {
        fn fetch_bonus(&self, hit: &CrossGroupFusedHit) -> BonusEntries;
